        <div class="reveal text-center relative" style="--delay: 4;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#2563EB] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-display font-bold text-lg mx-auto mb-6 relative z-10 shadow-lg shadow-[#2563EB]/30">4</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-[#1F2937] text-lg mb-3">성과 검증</h3>
          <p class="text-[#1F2937]/55 text-sm leading-relaxed">정량적 KPI 기반으로 성과를 측정하고, 지속적인 개선 방안을 제시합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Clients -->
